So heroes has been our theme.

00:00:46.360 --> 00:00:50.376
And us, as the partner team,
it's very easy to convince us

00:00:50.376 --> 00:00:51.750
that you guys are
all the heroes.

00:00:51.750 --> 00:00:54.760
Our job is working
with all of you,

00:00:54.760 --> 00:00:56.870
bringing all of
your great feedback

00:00:56.870 --> 00:01:00.340
into the team at Google Play
and Google more broadly,

00:01:00.340 --> 00:01:02.100
and working with
you to adopt all

00:01:02.100 --> 00:01:06.330
of these exciting new products
that are being announced.

