00:17:56.370 --> 00:17:58.320
So we want to make sure
that there's-- Android is

00:17:58.320 --> 00:17:58.903
for everybody.

00:17:58.903 --> 00:18:01.422
And so it's going to be massive
reach in terms of casual.

00:18:01.422 --> 00:18:03.630
But we also have people who
